section: compiler
synopsis: Refactor `Set UnitId` to `UniqDSet UnitId` in the `ghc` library.
issues: #23335
mrs: !10337

description: {
  Sets of `UnitId` throughout the `ghc` library now use the deterministic
  `UniqDSet UnitId` (exposed as the `UnitIdSet` synonym) instead of
  `Data.Set.Set UnitId`.
}
